title: Mackenzie Cowell // 16
description:
When a 17-year-old girl goes missing in 2010, her small town in Washington is flipped upside down. Surveillance footage of her leaving her beauty school is quickly discovered and it leads police to an interesting suspect. But when they put him behind bars, people start to doubt his involvement in the crime. This is the case of Mackenzie Cowell.
